You are hungry! Let's cook a delicious meal. Check the cookbook in the kitchen for the recipe. Once done, enjoy your meal!

-= Kitchen =-
You've entered a kitchen. You start to take note of what's in the room.

Oh wow! Is that what I think it is? It is! It's a fridge. You can't wait to tell the folks at home about this! You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice an oven. You idly wonder how they came up with the name TextWorld for this place. It's pretty fitting. You can make out a table. But there isn't a thing on it. You make out a counter. The counter is vast. On the counter you can make out a sliced fried red potato, a chopped fried banana, a red apple, a raw yellow potato and a cookbook. Wow! Just like in the movies! You can make out a stove. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a stove? Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it.

There is a closed plain door leading north. You don't like doors? Why not try going south, that entranceway is not blocked by one.

Oh wow! Is that what I think it is? It is! It's a fridge. You can't wait to tell the folks at home about this! You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice an oven. You idly wonder how they came up with the name TextWorld for this place. It's pretty fitting. You can make out a table. But there isn't a thing on it. You make out a counter. The counter is vast. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a stove? Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it.

There is a closed plain door leading north. You don't like doors? Why not try going south, that entranceway is not blocked by one.

You are hungry! Let's cook a delicious meal. Check the cookbook in the kitchen for the recipe. Once done, enjoy your meal!

-= Kitchen =-
You've entered a kitchen. You start to take note of what's in the room.

Oh wow! Is that what I think it is? It is! It's a fridge. You can't wait to tell the folks at home about this! You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice an oven. You idly wonder how they came up with the name TextWorld for this place. It's pretty fitting. You can make out a table. But there isn't a thing on it. You make out a counter. The counter is vast. On the counter you can make out a sliced fried red potato, a chopped fried banana, a red apple, a raw yellow potato and a cookbook. Wow! Just like in the movies! You can make out a stove. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a stove? Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it.

There is a closed plain door leading north. You don't like doors? Why not try going south, that entranceway is not blocked by one.

You are hungry! Let's cook a delicious meal. Check the cookbook in the kitchen for the recipe. Once done, enjoy your meal!

-= Kitchen =-
You've entered a kitchen. You start to take note of what's in the room.

Oh wow! Is that what I think it is? It is! It's a fridge. You can't wait to tell the folks at home about this! You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice an oven. You idly wonder how they came up with the name TextWorld for this place. It's pretty fitting. You can make out a table. But there isn't a thing on it. You make out a counter. The counter is vast. On the counter you can make out a sliced fried red potato, a chopped fried banana, a red apple, a raw yellow potato and a cookbook. Wow! Just like in the movies! You can make out a stove. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a stove? Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it.

There is a closed plain door leading north. You don't like doors? Why not try going south, that entranceway is not blocked by one.

Oh wow! Is that what I think it is? It is! It's a fridge. You can't wait to tell the folks at home about this! You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice an oven. You idly wonder how they came up with the name TextWorld for this place. It's pretty fitting. You can make out a table. But there isn't a thing on it. You make out a counter. The counter is vast. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a stove? Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it.

There is a closed plain door leading north. You don't like doors? Why not try going south, that entranceway is not blocked by one.

You are hungry! Let's cook a delicious meal. Check the cookbook in the kitchen for the recipe. Once done, enjoy your meal!

-= Kitchen =-
You've entered a kitchen. You start to take note of what's in the room.

Oh wow! Is that what I think it is? It is! It's a fridge. You can't wait to tell the folks at home about this! You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice an oven. You idly wonder how they came up with the name TextWorld for this place. It's pretty fitting. You can make out a table. But there isn't a thing on it. You make out a counter. The counter is vast. On the counter you can make out a sliced fried red potato, a chopped fried banana, a red apple, a raw yellow potato and a cookbook. Wow! Just like in the movies! You can make out a stove. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a stove? Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it.

There is a closed plain door leading north. You don't like doors? Why not try going south, that entranceway is not blocked by one.

-= Kitchen =-
You've entered a kitchen. You start to take note of what's in the room.

Oh wow! Is that what I think it is? It is! It's a fridge. You can't wait to tell the folks at home about this! You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice an oven. You idly wonder how they came up with the name TextWorld for this place. It's pretty fitting. You can make out a table. But there isn't a thing on it. You make out a counter. The counter is vast. On the counter you can make out a sliced fried red potato, a chopped fried banana, a red apple, a raw yellow potato and a cookbook. Wow! Just like in the movies! You can make out a stove. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a stove? Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it.

There is a closed plain door leading north. You don't like doors? Why not try going south, that entranceway is not blocked by one.

You are hungry! Let's cook a delicious meal. Check the cookbook in the kitchen for the recipe. Once done, enjoy your meal!

-= Kitchen =-
You've entered a kitchen. You start to take note of what's in the room.

Oh wow! Is that what I think it is? It is! It's a fridge. You can't wait to tell the folks at home about this! You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice an oven. You idly wonder how they came up with the name TextWorld for this place. It's pretty fitting. You can make out a table. But there isn't a thing on it. You make out a counter. The counter is vast. On the counter you can make out a sliced fried red potato, a chopped fried banana, a red apple, a raw yellow potato and a cookbook. Wow! Just like in the movies! You can make out a stove. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a stove? Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it.

There is a closed plain door leading north. You don't like doors? Why not try going south, that entranceway is not blocked by one.

-= Kitchen =-
You've entered a kitchen. You start to take note of what's in the room.

Oh wow! Is that what I think it is? It is! It's a fridge. You can't wait to tell the folks at home about this! You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice an oven. You idly wonder how they came up with the name TextWorld for this place. It's pretty fitting. You can make out a table. But there isn't a thing on it. You make out a counter. The counter is vast. On the counter you can make out a sliced fried red potato, a chopped fried banana, a red apple, a raw yellow potato and a cookbook. Wow! Just like in the movies! You can make out a stove. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a stove? Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it.

There is a closed plain door leading north. You don't like doors? Why not try going south, that entranceway is not blocked by one.
